snippet.title: Deadline Hollywood
snippet.description:
The YouTube home for Deadline Hollywood, the premier online news site following the business of Hollywood. We break all the news about the business of movies, TV, media and tech companies, Oscars and Emmys, the fast-growing business of YouTube MCNs and much more. Visit http://www.deadline.com for more. 

Have a tip? Send it to editors@deadline.com
